column5: Vacation rental house is in a quiet central location, perfect for winter Texans. Minutes away from Conn Brown Harbor, Rockport and Port Aransas Beaches. 1700 + sq ft, 3 Bdrms plus Sun Room, 2 Baths, and Sleeps 10. Relax and Enjoy the View from the Screened-in-Porch. Booking by week only June thru Oct , Nov. thru March booking by month only - competitively priced.
